title: STORM Of The CENTURY: The Tale of the Tape
body_text: ECD will soon be hit by its largest and most destructive storm in recent memory when arguably the two most recognize Goddesses wage a 1-on-1 war for the very first time. The informative "Tale of the Tape" tells all as we await this Saturday's forthcoming clash:
